  "prompt": "What is the best phone under 12k currently?",
  "response": "As of the latest information available, there are several phones priced under 12,000 INR that offer excellent features and performance. Here are a few options you might consider:\n\n1. **Realme Narzo 30A**: Known for its strong battery life and decent performance courtesy of the MediaTek Helio G85 processor.\n\n2. **Redmi 10 Prime**: Offers a balanced performance with a MediaTek Helio G88 processor, a large battery, and a 90Hz display.\n\n3. **Poco C3**: Provides good value for money with a MediaTek Helio G35 processor and a large display.\n\n4. **Samsung Galaxy M12**: Comes with a 90Hz display and a capable Exynos 850 processor along with a quad-camera setup at the rear.\n\n5. **Infinix Hot 10S**: Features a MediaTek Helio G85 processor with a high-refresh-rate display, making it a good choice for gaming and media consumption.\n\nThese models are strong contenders in this price segment as of the latest updates. It's a good idea to verify the most recent models and prices, as new releases can shift the landscape quickly. Always check for the latest reviews and user feedback to make an informed decision based on your specific needs and preferences.",
